            <h1>Final project proposal</h1>
            
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            
            <p>Lil Rascal Skates</p>
            
            <p>Lil Rascal Skates is a skateboard shop in Redondo Beach, California. It is in the sporting goods business. Lil Rascal's was established in 2016 and offers an assortment of skate-related goods: skateboard decks, trucks, wheels, and clothing from everyone's favorite skate brands. While the company is a staple of the Redondo Beach community, it is seeking to expand into e-commerce.</p>
            
            <h2>Target audience</h2>
            
            <p>The target audience is creative individuals between ages 18-25 who are looking to buy quality skateboard parts at a reasonable price. They are interested in skate culture and the arts and music that correspond.</p>
           
            <p>Their primary task is to shop skateboard stuff, whether that be skateboard parts or apparel. Additionally, a goal of theirs would be to compare prices, features and reviews of certain products compared to their competitors.</p>
            
